      • process

        public boolean process​(java.lang.String input)
                throws java.lang.Error
        Processes a sequence of commands. commands muust be followed by a ";" A command can be: M: moves forward R: turns right C: puts 1 chip B: puts 1 balloon c: picks 1 balloon b: picks 1 chip P: pops 1 balloon G(x,y): goes to position x,y d : d is a digit: jumps d squares forward
        Parameters:
        input - string of commands separated by commas to be interpreted. (i.e. RRG(3,3)BCM)
        Throws:
        java.lang.Error
